column9: precedence over controller cmd_vel and nav

The original publishing frequency was at whatever rate the frontend published data, which I benchmarked to be at around 70-80hz (the frontend js event loop is the bottleneck for publishing rate, basically what vue can re-render at). I have locked this at 60 to be manageable and consistent with nav, let me know if change is needed
